OL,7,FThe mother of a soldier from Crawley
OL,8,Fin West Sussex, who served in Iraq
OL,9,Fsays the military let her son down by
OL,10,Fnot doing more to help his mental
OL,11,Fhealth.
OL,13,FAeran Taylor suffered from post-
OL,14,Ftraumatic stress disorder and died
OL,15,Ffrom an accidental overdose in October
OL,16,F2023.
