OL,7,FHe was dismissed from the army after
OL,8,Ftaking drugs but an inquest found
OL,9,Fthere wasn't any clinical assessment
OL,10,Fof his condition after being
OL,11,Fdischarged.
OL,13,FThe Ministry of Defence say soldiers
OL,14,Fdo have access to treatment, but the
OL,15,Fcoroner in Aeran's case has warned a
OL,16,F'whole community of veterans' are at
OL,17,Frisk by the current support.
OL,19,FSpeaking to ITV Meridian, Aeran's mum,
OL,20,FCarol said: "They would have assessed
OL,21,Fhim.
