OL,7,F"He would have got the help he needed
OL,8,Fand he wouldn't have turned to drugs -
OL,9,Fnot hard drugs.
OL,11,F"He wouldn't have done that because he
OL,12,Fwould have had help from the start."
OL,14,FDespite working with a veteran's
OL,15,Fmental health charity, the former
OL,16,FRoyal Regiment of Fusiliers soldier
OL,17,Fhad not fully recovered from PTSD and
OL,18,Frelapsed into addiction.
