OL,7,FThe charity Mr Taylor worked with said
OL,8,Fit was "gravely concerned" by the
OL,9,Fcoroner's findings, and called on the
OL,10,FArmy to treat each failed drug test on
OL,11,Fa case-by-case basis.
OL,13,FOutlining his concerns in a prevention
OL,14,Fof future deaths report, Joseph
OL,15,FTurner, area coroner for West Sussex,
OL,16,FBrighton and Hove, said there was
OL,17,Fevidence of a lack of awareness of
OL,18,Fregimental welfare staff.
