OL,7,F"Those now serving may be more aware
OL,8,Fbut there appears to be a community of
OL,9,Fveterans at risk who may remain
OL,10,Funaware," the coroner said.
OL,12,F"There appears to remain a lack of
OL,13,Freadily available, fully funded, long
OL,14,Fterm rehabilitation and substance
OL,15,Fabuse recovery for veterans with PTSD,
OL,16,Fnotably for those only diagnosed well
OL,17,Fafter leaving the armed forces.
OL,19,F"In my opinion there is a risk that
OL,20,Ffuture deaths could occur unless
OL,21,Faction is taken," the coroner added.
