OL,8,Ffrom the Ministry of Defence, and had
OL,9,Fbeen engaging with his GP as well as a
OL,10,Fveteran's mental health charity called
OL,11,FCombat Stress.
OL,13,FIn a video he filmed with the charity
OL,14,Fin 2019, he said: "When I first left
OL,15,Fthe military I was really quite lost.
OL,17,F"I managed to hold down a job but even
OL,18,Fthat got too stressful for me, I was
OL,19,Fdepressed, I just locked myself away
OL,20,Fcompletely.
