OL,7,F"I wouldn't leave my flat for about
OL,8,Fsix months, I wouldn't answer the
OL,9,Fdoor, I was scared if my phone rang."
OL,11,FChloe Mackay, chief executive of
OL,12,FCombat Stress, said: "We were deeply
OL,13,Fsaddened at the passing of Aeran
OL,14,FTaylor and our thoughts remain with
OL,15,Fhis family and friends.
OL,17,F"Sadly we know from some of the
OL,18,Fveterans we treat that during their
OL,19,Fmilitary career they turned to illegal
OL,20,Fsubstances while battling with their
OL,21,Ftrauma.
