OL,7,F"What they needed was compassion and
OL,8,Fhelp in accessing mental health
OL,9,Ftreatment. We ask that the military
OL,10,Ftreats each failed drug test on a case-
OL,11,Fby-case basis, providing mental health
OL,12,Fsupport to those service personnel in
OL,13,Fneed.
OL,15,F"In addition, we are gravely concerned
OL,16,Fby the coroner's findings that there
OL,17,Fis a community of veterans at risk who
OL,18,Fremain unaware of the support
OL,19,Favailable to them.
